Dexia Has Enough Capital in Event of Recession, Mariani Says

-- B y   F a b i o   B e n e d e t t i - V a l e n t i n i
-- 
2011-10-10T08:16:24Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-10/dexia-has-enough-capital-in-event-of-recession-mariani-says.html
Dexia SA (DEXB) , which passed July European
Union stress tests, has enough capital to face a recession
scenario and writedowns on its holdings, Chief Executive Officer
Pierre Mariani said today on a conference call from Brussels.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Fabio Benedetti-Valentini at 
 fabiobv@bloomberg.net  